lace de la R√©publique. Nous participerons √† la mise en place d&#8217;un espace convivial d√©di√©e aux enfants et aux parents, avec les lectures organis√©es par certains de nos membres.</p>\n<p class=\"p3\">Par ce geste simple, contribuez √† l&#8217;occupation pacifique de la Place et permettez aux enfants de faire l&#8217;exp√©rience de la Nuit Debout !</p>\n<p class=\"p3\"><img class=\" wp-image-129 aligncenter\" src=\"http://biblio-debout.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/mouton-171x300.png\" alt=\"mouton\" width=\"198\" height=\"347\" /></p>\n<p class=\"p3\">\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:142:\"http://biblio-debout.org/index.php/2016/05/07/dimanche-69-mars-8-mai-portez-des-livres-jeunesse-pour-contribuer-a-enfants-parents-debout/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"Dimanche 69 mars (8 mai), la BiblioDebout organise un d√©bat sur les Communs\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:119:\"http://biblio-debout.org/index.php/2016/05/07/dimanche-69-mars-8-mai-la-bibliodebout-organise-un-debat-sur-les-communs/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\